 Missions is used to select:
----------------------------
 Demo Flight
 Airplanes
 Locations
 Formations
 Races
 Flight Training

Once you have selected a mission, location, and plane... The simulation
begins. Here are some simple instructions on how to take off from the 
airfield.
 
  step 1 -> Hit F2 to make flying the plane/jet a snap.
  step 2 -> If using joystick hit the button to place your flashing box
            over the small white crosshair.(if using mouse then just
            move your flashing box over the crosshair).
  step 3 -> Use the 1 through 0 keys to adjust your speed. A good
            take-off speed is the (8 key).
  step 4 -> Pull staight back on the controller you are using 
            (mouse/joystick), but not too far just under the bottom
            of the plane! And it should take off. 
  step 5 -> Once in mid-air hit (G key) to retract the gear. Then
            to fly the plane just move your controller in small movements
            around the small crosshair. You will be moving the flashing box
            so use this to control flight!

