 Key Commands:
--------------
  F1 -> Cockpit View
  F2 -> Rear View of plane/jet
  F3 -> Tower View
  F4 -> Looking down at plane/jet
  F5 -> Far away view
  F6 -> View from another plane/jet already in the sky
  F7 -> Satillite View
  
  The arrow Keys -> Pan around the view you have selected (F1-F7)

  1 - 0 -> 1 slowest speed and 0 is the fastest speed
  -   + -> (-) is to decrease speed (single step) (+) to speed up.
 
  ESC -> Escapes to Main Menu to select another plane/jet or all
         together new mission/race.

  W -> Turn the realism of wind ON/OFF
  E -> Flaps back
  F -> Flaps foward
  P -> Pause
  G -> Gear up/down
  H -> Heading ON/OFF
  
  ] -> (single step) pan up
  ' -> (single step) pan down
  : -> (single step) pan left
  [ -> (single step) pan right

  Z -> Move pointer setter to the left  (from cockpit view).
  X -> Move pointer setter to the right (from cockpit view).
  
  SPACEBAR -> Re-center flashing box to center of crosshair!

